metadata.name: Oyster Tree
metadata.description:
Cherished though they perish and fall off one by one. 
Piles of shells make mounds of pearls and emus kick through them all. 

An abundance of oysters! 

Minted for AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC hosted by Superchief and Exquisite Workers 

AI Animation & Music & Poetry & Performance by Laurence Fuller 
@laurencefuller
